@node MAIN "BBClock"
                                        @{b}@{u}BBClock@{uu}@{ub}

Welcome to BBClock, a new Workbench clock based on the look and feel of Backclock, but
supporting more configuration options. Options available with BBClock are:-

* All colours are individually customisable
* Transparent or solid clock face (Not the window)
* With solid window, optional 3D look
* Show or hide second hand
* Show or hide second markers
* Configure colours of hour/quarter and second markers separately
* MUI prefs program supporting realtime updating of the clock
* Very low CPU usage
* Fully OS friendly

The only Backclock option not currently supported is the LCD option. If you really want it,
let @{"me" link AUTHOR} know.

OK - so tell me more:-

@{"Why" link WHY}
@{"Requirements" link REQUIREMENTS}
@{"Installation" link INSTALLATION}
